 indeed to study the reasons and\nconsequences of a theory of particles with variable mass in the context of\nwider studies still in progress on QW.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Oct 2017 21:24:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Oct 2019 23:07:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-21"}
