MP freeze-in production rate\nleading to a natural and predicting scenario for the studies of the dark matter\nin the hidden sector.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Oct 2017 03:13:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 29 Oct 2017 04:31:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 10 May 2018 16:42:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-11"}
