eavy isotopes of Zn. Taken together, these\nlines of evidence strongly indicate that heated CM and CR chondrites incurred\nopen system heating, stripping them of water and volatiles concomitantly,\nduring post-accretionary shock impact(s).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Oct 2017 07:12:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-19"}
