ively a family of\n$2+1$d Dirac fermion patches, which leads to a non-analytic $(B^2-E^2)^{3/4}$\nQED action in the vicinity of the Dirac line.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Oct 2017 14:22:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Nov 2017 15:35:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-31"}
